<plot>A young divorced woman living in Mexico City seeks justice after her apartment is robbed. In the midst of a time and place where people are seemingly helpless against the many crimes, and the state bureaucracy is completely ineffective in prosecuting or preventing crimes, Eugenia refuses to submit to the apathy of the authorities in pursuing her case. The movie reflects the reality of urban crime in a place like Mexico City, where citizens must each take responsibility for ensuring social justice prevails.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?022529</url></doc>
